{
  "texts": [
    "In total, 957 Ae.",
    "tauschii and 59 wheat landraces accessions reached the quality threshold of a coverage higher than fivefold after trimming and were used for SNP calling.",
    "The SNP data set was used for phylogenetic, ancestry, and nucleotide diversity analyses.",
    "The phylogenetic tree was built from the filtered SNPs using vcfkit (v0.1.6) 80 with the UPGMA algorithm.",
    "Ancestry analysis was performed using the sNMF (Fast and Efficient Estimation of Individual Ancestry Coefficients) approach available in the LEA R package (v3.10.2) 81."
  ]
}